{"tid":2122346,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍天盛苑法團抗爭 7月25號再開!","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:28:36.000Z","uid":120355,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5713e02375b4361a6e243812ace7ca89dd7b0b","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"之前既POST<br />\n天水圍天盛苑業主大會12月3日被民主陣線成員甘天成(天盛業委主席)恐嚇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1760285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1760285/page/1</a><br />\n天盛苑法團戰後繼 (文長注意) 法團儲備清空大計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1776685/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1776685/page/1</a><br />\n天盛12月3罷業法團大會 出現咗1張票=700户業主嘅荒謬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767932/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767932/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係12月業主大會失敗後，我地已經再次係２月收到５％招開業主大會<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kW7EJcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkW7EJcT.jpg&h=18168c27&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n但係法團多次以武漢肺炎為理由不斷推遲開會<br />\n<br />\n好啦最後推到決定<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"large\">７月２５號</span></strong></span>先開會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQdMoe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQdMoe1.jpg&h=0d4f08da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知呢班委員７月１號<strong><span class=\"red\">集體辭職</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7chuTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7chuTH.jpg&h=9ad38848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">辭職有咩問題？ </span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">好大問題！<br />\n首先雖然佢地辭哂職，但係成個屋苑既資金而然係佢地手上<br />\n只係無權力使用，即係仲ＨＯＬＤ住哂所有資金<br />\n呢家管理公司營運資金只剩返７月８月份既運作資金<br />\n無錢隨時走</span></strong><br />\n（目前是新上任管理公司，係７月１號後上任）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係今日７月２４號朝早<br />\n侯選法團話管理公司收到電話要求取消大會<br />\n話驚肺炎會大爆發<br />\n不過係非本苑居民ＷＯ<br />\n唔通係。。。？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PYksHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PYksHo.png&h=300b1c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><br />\n天盛人聽日一定要出黎呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"16698819e2eaebb92185ef5f4f2203361bc0d2a3","tid":2122346,"uid":66392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac911e8d6ad969b79d7da9fad5659414ba81cc1e","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXVu5xe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXVu5xe.png&h=0d538dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zhxmcce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhxmcce.png&h=f7dc240b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本苑藍絲理論<br />\n貼堂"},{"pid":"131a7cb551679668658d8b76b6c3af67781198f7","tid":2122346,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"限聚令唔影響? 班仆街狗又出嚟"},{"pid":"3a3e30ad72de8418af9cd41b4e5bf82a56bf8622","tid":2122346,"uid":189132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc36f21dbc6a7c444bb017e88b2987a1d200f4dd","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131a7cb551679668658d8b76b6c3af67781198f7","tid":2122346,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"限聚令唔影響? 班仆街狗又出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"7.25週年大會 - 監察組呼籲出席投票之聲明<br />\n&bull; 監察組非常重視疫情對居民的影響，我們要求富城採取有效措施，在開會前需要對會場進行徹底消毒，出席者入場需要測量體溫，擦搓手液之後，才可以進場，而且必須全程帶口罩，會場內座位也是需要按照規定保持距離，而投票過程應該以流水方式分散進行，總之必須採取最嚴格防疫措施，以保證週年大會在安全和不違反限聚令底下進行。<br />\n&bull; 監察組向富城了解過，民政署及法團委任律師都落實出席本次週年大會。<br />\n&bull; 監察組也有向獅子會何德心小學了解過，校方表示學校是私人地方，從來沒有以「公眾地方」名義借出場地，這一點校方都希望我們街坊群組明白，並為學校澄清。<br />\n&bull; 另外，學校已經詢問教育局星期六的大會是否可以舉行，教育局並無反對，教育局提醒學校須做足防疫措施，以免疫情傳播。學校亦曾經要求管理公司詢問民政事務處，民政事務處亦是無反對，學校一直與管理公司緊密聯絡，要求管理公司必須做好當日嘅防疫措施。<br />\n&bull; 監察組完全明白居民對於召開週年大會的憂慮，不過正如大家都知道，委員會已經集體辭職，法團現在處於停擺狀態，如果7.25（本星期六）的會議無法進行，物業管理服務將只能夠提供有限度服務，對廣大居民影響十分嚴重的，我們還是呼籲業主出席投票，選出新一屆委員會，盡快接手法團職務，保證屋苑持續良好運作。"},{"pid":"a4e77219bd6bcd3a634e37743fe4aa416a7f9501","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">上一次召喚極都無記者肯黎<br />\n<br />\n再次試下召喚記者先</span>!</span>"},{"pid":"c3df076fbce6a33bef5cbf11dfc427387b8e3f1b","tid":2122346,"uid":217452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"Push notifications"},{"pid":"9ed02c016150c90c66819c65e2aa60eba5535f06","tid":2122346,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07515383ea92d383d0f3130d6c5ffae92bc788aa","tid":2122346,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"24ef89d7e67324bb7a6512bdb48beb09a6fbab25","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"b59ead0dd2a5185f55b986e942f1af5a844a6c82","tid":2122346,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"叫天水<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">圍</span></strong></span>連線坐陣如何"},{"pid":"662c5ce9f5735e884177c42741b74a24b9e0653c","tid":2122346,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59ead0dd2a5185f55b986e942f1af5a844a6c82","tid":2122346,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"叫天水<span clas